transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Ya hello, Sikandar ji kaise hain aap? Hello Sikandar ji kaise hain aap?
Customer: Bas badhiya hai.
Executive: Haan badhiya hai bolo.
Executive: Sir actually aapka catalog aapne ticket raise kiya tha na aapka catalog aap sahi karana chah rahe the.
Customer: Catalog kya hai dhandha kam to mil hi nahi raha aapke yahan se koi dhang ki lead nahi aa rahi hai.
Executive: Koi baat nahi abhi aapko teen mahine hue hain na dheere dheere work ho raha hai.
Customer: Teen mahine kya hua mere ko kya pichle saal pichle saal chalai hai maine dedh do saal.
Executive: Bilkul main samajh rahi hu sir aapki baat ko lekin dekho ab aapki complaint mein aapka complaint mujhe mila sir maine work kiya hai na aapki profile par dekho aapke catalog maine ke sath kar diya hai aapke catalog mein jo bhi aapki problems thi na jo bhi aapke chair vagaira jitni bhi photos thi sab maine laga di hai unki product ki mapping ache se kar di hai theek hai specification add kar di hai abhi maine aapka profile kal hi complete kiya hai sir theek hai aap check kar lo aapka profile ab bilkul complete ho gaya thoda wait karo sir dheere dheere aapke pass by leads achi aane lag jayegi aapko already service liye hue teen mahine ho gaye hain na sir.
Customer: Theek hai theek hai main thodi der baad wapas call karta hu main aapko.
Executive: Haan haan sir bilkul lekin aapka jo ticket raise hua tha use close kar du na main.
